OL,3,CWelsh football star Aaron Ramsey
OL,4,Cbecomes new Oxford United head coach
OL,6,FFormer Wales captain and Arsenal
OL,7,Fmidfielder Aaron Ramsey has been named
OL,8,Fas the next head coach for Oxford
OL,9,FUnited's men's team.
OL,11,FThe 35-year old will arrive at Kassam
OL,12,FStadium following the sacking of
OL,13,FOxford United's previous manager, Matt
OL,14,FBloomfield.
OL,16,FFor Wales, Ramsey scored 21 goals in
OL,17,F86 appearances and played at three
OL,18,Fmajor tournaments, including a key
OL,19,Frole in the country's historic run to
OL,20,Fthe Euro 2016 semi-finals.
