OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1782314307
OL,3,CWelsh football star Aaron Ramsey
OL,4,Cbecomes new Oxford United head coach
OL,6,FThe midfielder briefly managed Cardiff
OL,7,FCity in an interim role at the end of
OL,8,Fthe 2024-2025 season.
OL,10,FSpeaking after his appointment, Aaron
OL,11,FRamsey said: "It's an honour and
OL,12,Fprivilege to be appointed Head Coach
OL,13,Fof Oxford United.
OL,15,F"From my discussions with the Club, I
OL,16,Fcan sense the ambition and desire for
OL,17,Fsuccess, which gives me great
OL,18,Fexcitement about this opportunity.
