OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1782314307
OL,3,CWelsh football star Aaron Ramsey
OL,4,Cbecomes new Oxford United head coach
OL,6,F"This is a moment I have been
OL,7,Fpreparing for over many years. I've
OL,8,Fplayed under some of the best managers
OL,9,Fin the game and experienced high-
OL,10,Fpressure environments throughout my
OL,11,Fcareer.
OL,13,FI want to use what I've learnt to
OL,14,Fbring a culture of high standards,
OL,15,Fprofessionalism and work ethic to this
OL,16,Ftalented group of players."
